# secrets
.env
.env.local

# Proprietary cast assets — never commit (incident 2026-07-05).
# Voices are account-specific; mint locally with `npm run mint-voice`.
# Only the bundled "wren" sample cast is allow-listed below;
# voices.json stays ignored (account-specific voice_ids, rewritten on every mint).
voices/*.mp3
voices/*.wav
voices/voices.json
profiles/*.md
environments/*.md
elements/references/*
!voices/README.md
!**/.gitkeep
# — bundled sample cast: "Wren" (clip only; users mint their own voice_id) —
!profiles/wren.md
!elements/references/wren-*
!voices/wren.mp3
# — bundled sample environment: "Neon City" (users' own environments stay local) —
!environments/neon-city.md

